title: Breaking Bad - Season Four (MP4)
description:
This is the fourth season of breaking bad converted to MP4 for the purposes of watching on my Vita. After spending an hour or more converting each one, it seemed someone else may appreciate me saving them the time should they have a preference or need for MP4 format.

The file size is small, but the show looks great on the Vita. How it may look on a larger screen someone else would have to tell you (if my computer ran well enough to run it,I would not have bothered converting it), but I would imagine it more than watchable.

Unlike my previous uploads, the spanish dialogue has hard english subs. This season is censored (which as far as I can tell consisted of reducing about four 'fucks' to 'f---'), and also has AMC's 'previously on Breaking Bad...' recaps at the beginning of every episode

I am not going to release a half season, so don't expect season 5 until it is all out. When it is, I will upload both a season 5 pack, and a complete pack. Between now and then I will try to replace the earlier seasons with ones that are hard subbed, and the fourth with one that is uncensored.
